data.description: Welcome home to this 4 bed, 4 bath, 2 car garage that has 3,028 sq ft.!! The main level of this home offers lots of windows that gives a ton of natural lighting and high ceilings in the living room. This home greets you with a flex space and a great size kitchen that flows into a spacious living room that is great for entertaining. The enclosed patio on the main can be used for anything your heart desires. The upstairs has 3 great size bedrooms along with 2 full bathrooms and a loft that is perfect for that extra hangout space. The finished walkout basement offers a covered patio, great size bedroom with a full bath and a family room that is perfect for game day or the teenager that wants their own space. This home has 2 hot water heaters and the roof is going to be replaced soon.
